# Encore environment variables — NAMES ONLY, never commit values.
# Copy to .env.local for local development (gitignored).

# The Convex deployment URL the client connects to.
# Public by design — safe to expose in the built client.
# Set automatically in .env.local by `npx convex dev`.
EXPO_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=

# --- Convex server-side env vars (set with `npx convex env set NAME value`,
# --- NOT in any local file; listed here for documentation only):
#
# MUSICBRAINZ_USER_AGENT   e.g. "Encore/0.1 (you@example.com)" — required by
#                          MusicBrainz API etiquette for the pre-bake action.
